            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="small-12 columns" style="padding: 0;">
          <div class="profile-social">
            <ul class="social">
              <li>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Ellebkey" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/Ellebkey" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://github.com/Ellebkey" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-github"></i></a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ellebkey/" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i></a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/joelbarranco/" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin"></i></a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="small-12 columns"  style="padding: 0;">
          <div class="section-txt-btn">
            <p>Hello! I’m Joel Barranco. FullStack Developer specializing in node.js and angularjs. Experienced with all stages of the development cycle for dynamic web projects. Well-versed in numerous programming languages including JavaScript, Python, and C. Background in computer vision and machine learning.</p>
